    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "Well-kept older car in good condition and ready to enjoy as a solid driver. It presents nicely overall, with a clean appearance inside and out, and it appears to have been maintained better than many cars of similar age. This is not being represented as a show car, but it is a respectable, usable example that should appeal to someone looking for a clean older vehicle they can drive and enjoy with confidence.",
