    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and priced to move, this vehicle offers a straightforward opportunity for a handy buyer, commuter, or project-car shopper. It shows age and wear consistent with an older used vehicle, but presents a practical chance to get into a car at an accessible price point. A sensible option for someone who values affordability and potential.",
      "price": 4900.0,
