      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels with plenty of potential? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a great opportunity for someone handy, a first-time buyer on a budget, or anyone who wants a solid project without spending a fortune. It has honest wear consistent with age and use, and it\u2019s being priced to reflect that. If you want something inexpensive you can put your own touch on, this could be a really worthwhile buy. Come take a look and see if it\u2019s the right fit for you.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Driver-ready project with solid enthusiast appeal. The powertrain pulls well, the transmission engages as it should, and the chassis still feels like a usable platform with plenty of life left for the next owner. This is not a showroom car, but it has the kind of mechanical honesty buyers look for in an affordable daily, budget build, or weekend revival. Expect cosmetic wear and age-related imperfections consistent with a well-used vehicle, but the fundamentals make it worth a serious look. Priced to move for someone who wants capability and value without paying collector money.",
      "price": 7900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    }
